title: FOIA Request - Fernando Uriel Arroyos Homicide

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

Victim: Fernando Uriel Arroyos (homicide investigation)

Perpetrators: 
Luis Alfredo De La Rosa Rios 
Ernesto Cisneros 
Jesse Contreras 
Haylee Marie Grisham

Date of incident: January 10, 2022

Records to be requested:
-Incident report
-911 call
-crime scene photos
-crime scene video
-Body cam: footage of arrest (if available)
-Police notes
-video/audio of police interrogation
-autopsy report

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Jennifer Solorio

communications.subject: Texas Public Information Act Request: FOIA Request - Christopher Jacob Carrizal
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Texas Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

This is a request under the Freedom of Information Act requesting copies of all records, including video, audio, emails, texts, and other similar documents, whether sent from or received on official or personal equipment related to any investigation into Christopher Jacob Carrizal regarding an incident that took place at Twin Peaks on May 17, 2015.

To help narrow your search, Carrizal's DOB is 11/13/1981.
 
This request includes but is not limited to the following: any crime scene photos/videos, 911 calls, dashcam or body camera footage, cell phone video, case files, incident reports, police reports, interrogation videos/audio, autopsy reports, police interrogation video for other people involved in the shootout, and police video of arrests.  

I am a producer with Vice News, this request is made for the purpose of news gathering and not for commercial use.
 
I request a waiver of all fees since this request is being made in the interest of the public and will contribute significantly to the public’s understanding of the operations and activities related to this former public official’s activities. 
 
I request an expedited processing of this request as this information provides great value to public interest and thus is time sensitive.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Jennifer Solorio
